          "title": "Day 1",
          "text": "<b><i class='far fa-clock'></i> 18:00 - 20:00</b> - check in at Casa Petri Roșia Montană - accommodation and get to know each other. <br><b><i class='far fa-clock'></i> 21:00</b> - Dinner"
        },
        {
          "title": "Day 2",
          "text": "<b><i class='far fa-clock'></i> 09:00</b> - Breakfast <br><b><i class='far fa-clock'></i> 10:00 - 16:00 - Guided Tour Daffodil meadow</b> <br> From Rosia Montana will go to a magic place from Carpathians mountains - the protected area 'Negrileasa Apuseni' to discover the daffodil meadow. The amazing landscape and the daffodil smell will make an unique experience from this trip. There are a couple of ways to get there (according to the group preference and weather): by car (~30min) followed by a 2 hour walk or by bike on the country road (~4h) – if you don't come with your own bike you can rent one from us.",
